---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout
  title="Quotient Cloud — Measured cloud. Quantified savings."
  description="Independent cloud advisory. We help enterprises measure, optimise, and govern their cloud across infrastructure, licensing, security, architecture, and adoption strategy."
>

<header class="site">
  <div class="wrap">
    <a class="qc-lockup" href="#">
      <span class="qc-badge"><span class="qc" style="font-size:17px"><span class="q">Q</span><span class="bar"></span><span class="c">C</span></span></span>
      <span class="word"><span class="l">quotient</span><span class="l">cloud</span></span>
    </a>
    <nav>
      <a href="#market">Market</a>
      <a href="#services">Services</a>
      <a href="#qscore">Q-Score</a>
      <a href="#process">Process</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-nav-cta">Get in touch</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="eyebrow reveal">Independent cloud advisory&nbsp;&nbsp;·&nbsp;&nbsp;Azure&nbsp;&nbsp;·&nbsp;&nbsp;AWS</div>
    <h1 class="reveal">Measured cloud.<br><em>Quantified savings.</em></h1>
    <p class="lead reveal">Quotient Cloud helps enterprises measure, optimise, and govern their cloud environments — across infrastructure, licensing, security, architecture, and adoption strategy. Every engagement produces a quantified outcome, tracked through the Cloud Quotient Score&#8482;.</p>
    <div class="ctas reveal">
      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get in touch &#8594;</a>
      <a href="#services" class="btn btn-secondary">See our services</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hstats stagger">
      <div class="hstat"><div class="lbl">Savings guarantee</div><div class="val">2&#215;</div></div>
      <div class="hstat"><div class="lbl">Service pillars</div><div class="val">5</div></div>
      <div class="hstat"><div class="lbl">Methodology</div><div class="val">Q-Score&#8482;</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="market" style="background:var(--qc-paper-2)">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sh reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">The market reality</div>
      <h2>Cloud is growing fast. <span class="hem">So is the need for oversight.</span></h2>
      <p>Cloud and technology are accelerating globally &#8212; driven by AI, data analytics, hybrid infrastructure, and digital transformation. Enterprises across every industry are expanding their cloud footprint to stay competitive. As environments grow in scale and complexity, structured oversight of spend, architecture, security, and vendor decisions becomes essential to realising the value of that investment.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mstats stagger">
      <div class="mstat"><div class="big">$1T+</div><div class="desc">Global cloud market size projected in 2026 &#8212; growing at 21% year on year</div><div class="src">Gartner Cloud Forecast 2026</div></div>
      <div class="mstat"><div class="big">33%</div><div class="desc">Cloud as a share of total enterprise IT budget &#8212; and rising every year</div><div class="src">Flexera State of the Cloud 2025</div></div>
      <div class="mstat"><div class="big">92%</div><div class="desc">Enterprises using multi-cloud strategy &#8212; driving complexity and the need for governance</div><div class="src">Synergy Research Group 2025</div></div>
    </div>
    <p class="reveal" style="margin-top:28px;font-size:15px;color:var(--qc-ink-70);line-height:1.6;max-width:72ch">Organisations that embed financial governance and independent advisory into their cloud practice consistently outperform those that do not. This is where Quotient Cloud adds measurable value.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="services">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sh reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">What we do</div>
      <h2>Five pillars. <span class="hem">Full lifecycle.</span></h2>
      <p>Every Quotient Cloud engagement falls under one of five pillars &#8212; covering the full lifecycle of cloud decision-making, from understanding what you currently spend to designing what you should build next.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pillars stagger">
      <div class="pillar p1"><div class="pnum">01</div><div class="pname">Audit</div><div class="pdesc">Analyse your existing cloud spend and identify exactly where money is leaking.</div></div>
      <div class="pillar p2"><div class="pnum">02</div><div class="pname">Save</div><div class="pdesc">Reduce what you pay for cloud infrastructure and SaaS licenses &#8212; measurably.</div></div>
      <div class="pillar p3"><div class="pnum">03</div><div class="pname">Secure</div><div class="pdesc">Independent review &#8212; CIS &#183; NIST &#183; ISO 27001 &#183; NCA &#183; SAMA &#183; TDRA &#183; PDPL.</div></div>
      <div class="pillar p4"><div class="pnum">04</div><div class="pname">Architect</div><div class="pdesc">Design new cloud infrastructure right before you commit to it.</div></div>
      <div class="pillar p5"><div class="pnum">05</div><div class="pname">Advise</div><div class="pdesc">Independent review of vendor proposals and cloud adoption decisions.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="pconn"><span class="dot"></span><span>Every pillar feeds your Cloud Quotient Score&#8482;</span><span class="dot"></span></div>

    <div style="margin-top:60px">
      <div class="eyebrow reveal" style="margin-bottom:20px">Engagement streams</div>
      <div class="streams">

        <div class="stream" id="s1a">
          <div class="srow" onclick="tog('s1a')"><div class="stag">Stream 1A</div><div class="stitle">Audit &amp; Basic Report</div><div class="stog">+</div></div>
          <div class="sbody">
            <div class="sgrid">
              <div class="scol"><h4>What we deliver</h4><ul><li>Current state review of your cloud environment</li><li>Cloud Quotient Score for the audited dimension</li><li>Findings summary with areas of concern</li><li>Savings potential identified at high level</li><li>Recommended next steps</li></ul></div>
              <div class="scol"><h4>Scope &amp; pricing</h4><p>Scoped per engagement based on environment size and complexity. Day rate basis &#8212; agreed upfront before engagement starts.</p><p class="snote">Small: 1&#8211;2 days &nbsp;&#183;&nbsp; Mid-market: 3&#8211;5 days &nbsp;&#183;&nbsp; Enterprise: 1&#8211;2 weeks</p><h4 style="margin-top:14px">Guarantee</h4><p>No guarantee &#8212; audit fee is charged for the work completed. The report will always show clear optimisation opportunities.</p></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="stream feat open" id="s1b">
          <div class="srow" onclick="tog('s1b')"><div class="stag">Stream 1B &nbsp;&#183;&nbsp; Most comprehensive</div><div class="stitle">Audit &amp; Detailed Optimisation Report</div><div class="stog">+</div></div>
          <div class="sbody">
            <div class="sgrid">
              <div class="scol"><h4>What we deliver</h4><ul><li>Full audit of the environment</li><li>Cloud Quotient Score for the dimension</li><li>Step-by-step optimisation plan</li><li>Resource-by-resource recommendations</li><li>License-by-license or user-by-user analysis</li><li>Expected savings per action with implementation sequence</li></ul></div>
              <div class="scol"><h4>Scope &amp; pricing</h4><p>Larger scope than 1A &#8212; detailed technical analysis requires more time. Audit fee plus optimisation report fee based on environment complexity. Agreed upfront before work begins.</p><h4 style="margin-top:14px">Guarantee</h4><p>2&#215; minimum guarantee applies &#8212; savings identified will be at least 2&#215; the audit fee per month.</p><div class="gpill">minimum savings guarantee</div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="stream" id="s2">
          <div class="srow" onclick="tog('s2')"><div class="stag">Stream 2</div><div class="stitle">Audit + Optimisation (Hands-On)</div><div class="stog">+</div></div>
          <div class="sbody">
            <div class="sgrid">
              <div class="scol"><h4>What we deliver</h4><ul><li>Full audit and Q-Score</li><li>Detailed optimisation plan</li><li>Hands-on implementation support alongside your team</li><li>Engagement continues until savings are confirmed on your bill</li></ul></div>
              <div class="scol"><h4>Pricing</h4><p>Audit fee (day rate, scoped upfront) plus an optimisation fee &#8212; a percentage of first month&#8217;s savings achieved.</p><p class="snote">Up to $10K/mo: 50% &nbsp;&#183;&nbsp; $10K&#8211;$50K: 40% &nbsp;&#183;&nbsp; $50K&#8211;$200K: 30% &nbsp;&#183;&nbsp; $200K+: 20%</p><h4 style="margin-top:14px">Guarantee</h4><p>2&#215; minimum guarantee &#8212; savings delivered will be at least 2&#215; the audit fee per month.</p><div class="gpill">minimum savings guarantee</div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="stream" id="s3">
          <div class="srow" onclick="tog('s3')"><div class="stag">Stream 3</div><div class="stitle">Architecture, Security &amp; Advisory</div><div class="stog">+</div></div>
          <div class="sbody">
            <div class="sgrid">
              <div class="scol"><h4>Services included</h4><ul><li>Vendor proposal review (1&#8211;2 days)</li><li>Security &amp; compliance review &#8212; small environment (3&#8211;5 days)</li><li>Security &amp; compliance review &#8212; enterprise (2&#8211;4 weeks)</li><li>Architecture design (1&#8211;2 weeks)</li><li>Cloud adoption roadmap (3&#8211;6 weeks)</li></ul></div>
              <div class="scol"><h4>Pricing</h4><p>Scoped per engagement. Day rate basis &#8212; scope and fee agreed in writing before work begins. Pure expertise. No outcome fee on this stream.</p><h4 style="margin-top:14px">Guarantee</h4><p>No savings guarantee on this stream &#8212; covers advisory and design work, not optimisation outcomes.</p></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
      <div class="gbanner reveal">
        <div class="gicon">&#10003;</div>
        <div class="gtext"><h3>2&#215; Minimum Savings Guarantee</h3><p>On Stream 1B and Stream 2 engagements, we guarantee that the savings identified and delivered will be at minimum 2&#215; the audit fee per month. The audit fee is always charged &#8212; it is independent, thorough work. The guarantee applies to the optimisation outcome.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<section id="qscore" class="dark">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sh reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">The Cloud Quotient Score&#8482;</div>
      <h2>One score. <span class="hem">Per engagement. Per pillar.</span></h2>
      <p>The Q-Score is our proprietary diagnostic tool. Every engagement produces an independent score for that dimension &#8212; giving you a clear, quantified view of where you stand. Scores are per pillar, per engagement. No forced composite.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="qlayout">
      <div class="reveal">
        <div class="qcard">
          <div class="qcard-hd"><span class="qtag">Sample client &#183; two engagements completed</span><span class="qtag">v1.0</span></div>
          <div class="qrow"><span class="dn">Cost Q-Score</span><div class="db"><i style="width:47%"></i></div><span class="dv">47</span><span class="qband bdev2">Developing</span></div>
          <div class="qrow"><span class="dn">Security Q-Score</span><div class="db"><i style="width:38%"></i></div><span class="dv">38</span><span class="qband bcrit2">Critical</span></div>
          <div class="qrow pend"><span class="dn">License Q-Score</span><div class="db"></div><span class="dv" style="color:var(--qc-muted)">&#8212;</span><span class="qband bpend">Not assessed</span></div>
          <div class="qrow pend"><span class="dn">Architecture Q-Score</span><div class="db"></div><span class="dv" style="color:var(--qc-muted)">&#8212;</span><span class="qband bpend">Not assessed</span></div>
          <div class="qrow pend"><span class="dn">Compliance Q-Score</span><div class="db"></div><span class="dv" style="color:var(--qc-muted)">&#8212;</span><span class="qband bpend">Not assessed</span></div>
          <div class="qfooter"><span>2 of 5 dimensions assessed</span><span>Quotient Cloud &#183; v1.0</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="qrt">Each engagement produces exactly one score &#8212; for the dimension we audited. A cost audit gives you a Cost Q-Score. A security review gives you a Security Q-Score. Scores accumulate naturally as you engage across pillars &#8212; never forced into a composite that obscures where the real issues are.</p>
        <div class="fblock"><b>Cost Q-Score</b> &#8212; cloud spend efficiency analysis<br><b>License Q-Score</b> &#8212; SaaS optimisation analysis<br><b>Security Q-Score</b> &#8212; posture vs CIS &#183; NIST &#183; NCA &#183; SAMA &#183; TDRA<br><b>Architecture Q-Score</b> &#8212; WAF alignment review<br><b>Compliance Q-Score</b> &#8212; regulatory framework mapping</div>
        <div class="bscale">
          <div class="bc2 bcrit3"><div class="rng">0 &#8211; 40</div><div class="lbl">Critical</div><div class="dsc">Immediate action needed</div></div>
          <div class="bc2 bdev3"><div class="rng">41 &#8211; 60</div><div class="lbl">Developing</div><div class="dsc">Clear improvement opportunity</div></div>
          <div class="bc2 bpro3"><div class="rng">61 &#8211; 80</div><div class="lbl">Proficient</div><div class="dsc">Well managed, targeted work</div></div>
          <div class="bc2 bopt3"><div class="rng">81 &#8211; 100</div><div class="lbl">Optimised</div><div class="dsc">Leading practice</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="process">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sh reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">How we work</div>
      <h2>Five steps. <span class="hem">No surprises.</span></h2>
      <p>Every engagement is scoped before it starts and delivered as agreed &#8212; no billable hours, no scope creep. Scope and fee are fixed in writing before any work begins.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="psteps stagger">
      <div class="pstep"><div class="psnum">01</div><div class="pst">Initial Conversation</div><div class="psd">We understand your environment, requirement, and objective. No charge for this conversation.</div></div>
      <div class="pstep act"><div class="psnum">02</div><div class="pst">Scope Agreement</div><div class="psd">We define exactly what will be delivered, how long it takes, and what it costs &#8212; in writing.</div></div>
      <div class="pstep"><div class="psnum">03</div><div class="pst">Engagement</div><div class="psd">We execute the work independently. Typically read-only access to cost and configuration data.</div></div>
      <div class="pstep act"><div class="psnum">04</div><div class="pst">Delivery</div><div class="psd">Written report, Q-Score, and recommendations. All output belongs to you.</div></div>
      <div class="pstep"><div class="psnum">05</div><div class="pst">Ongoing Retainer</div><div class="psd">Optional. Monthly advisory to maintain oversight and track Q-Score improvement.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="gbanner reveal">
      <div class="gicon">&#10003;</div>
      <div class="gtext"><h3>2&#215; Minimum Savings Guarantee</h3><p>On Stream 1B and Stream 2 engagements, we guarantee savings of at least 2&#215; the audit fee per month. The audit fee is always charged for the work completed. The guarantee applies to the optimisation outcome.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="background:var(--qc-paper-2)">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sh reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">Who we serve</div>
      <h2>From SME to <span class="hem">large enterprise.</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="serve reveal">
      <p>We work with <em>small and medium enterprises through to large organisations</em> looking to manage their cloud spending, optimise their environments, and adopt cloud technologies effectively. If you have a cloud environment and want a clear, independent view of how it is performing &#8212; we are the right conversation.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="contact" class="dark">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="clayout">
      <div class="reveal">
        <div class="eyebrow">Get in touch</div>
        <h2 class="chead">Every engagement begins with a conversation.</h2>
        <p class="clead">Tell us about your environment and what you want to achieve. We will tell you what we can deliver &#8212; and which engagement stream makes the most sense.</p>
        <a href="mailto:hello@quotientcloud.io" class="btn btn-primary">Send a message &#8594;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal">
        <div class="ccard">
          <div class="crow"><span class="k">Email</span><span class="v">hello@quotientcloud.io</span><span class="ar">&#8594;</span></div>
          <div class="crow"><span class="k">Website</span><span class="v">quotientcloud.io</span><span class="ar">&#8594;</span></div>
          <div class="crow"><span class="k">LinkedIn</span><span class="v">/company/quotient-cloud</span><span class="ar">&#8594;</span></div>
          <div class="crow"><span class="k">Book a call</span><span class="v">cal.com/quotient-cloud</span><span class="ar">&#8594;</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="ftop">
      <a class="qc-lockup" href="#">
        <span class="qc-badge"><span class="qc" style="font-size:17px"><span class="q">Q</span><span class="bar"></span><span class="c">C</span></span></span>
        <span class="word"><span class="l">quotient</span><span class="l">cloud</span></span>
      </a>
      <div class="flinks">
        <div><h5>Services</h5><ul><li><a href="#services">Audit</a></li><li><a href="#services">Save</a></li><li><a href="#services">Secure</a></li><li><a href="#services">Architect</a></li><li><a href="#services">Advise</a></li></ul></div>
        <div><h5>Methodology</h5><ul><li><a href="#qscore">Q-Score&#8482;</a></li><li><a href="#services">Streams</a></li><li><a href="#process">Process</a></li></ul></div>
        <div><h5>Contact</h5><ul><li><a href="mailto:hello@quotientcloud.io">hello@quotientcloud.io</a></li><li><a href="#contact">Book a call</a></li><li><a href="https://linkedin.com/company/quotient-cloud">LinkedIn</a></li></ul></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flegal"><span>&#169; 2026 Quotient Cloud &#183; Independent Cloud Advisory &#183; Azure &#183; AWS</span><span>Measured cloud. Quantified savings.</span></div>
  </div>
</footer>

<script>
function tog(id){const el=document.getElementById(id);const was=el.classList.contains('open');document.querySelectorAll('.stream').forEach(s=>s.classList.remove('open'));if(!was)el.classList.add('open');}
const obs=new IntersectionObserver(e=>{e.forEach(el=>{if(el.isIntersecting){el.target.classList.add('in');obs.unobserve(el.target)}})},{threshold:.08});
document.querySelectorAll('.reveal,.stagger').forEach(el=>obs.observe(el));
const hdr=document.querySelector('header.site');
window.addEventListener('scroll',()=>{hdr.style.background=window.scrollY>40?'rgba(6,9,15,.98)':'rgba(6,9,15,.94)';},{passive:true});
</script>

</Layout>
